  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Somehow, even though my husband was a psychologist-- he was not a clinical psychologist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was an experimental psychologist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So-- but I don't know that I would have talked to him about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- this was a part of my life that was past and that somehow should not impinge on the present, as I saw it at that time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I always look at children, to this day, and I think, you know, this child is eight, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and what you do with an eight-year-old?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, we got over that period.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the problem became less with my subsequent children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess I learned how to be a mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or I think I learned how to be a mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You'd have to ask my children [LAUGHS] how good a mother I was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, I guess, like all survivors I was a very, very protective mother, you know, terrified if they were a minute late and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very strict about the times they were allowed to go out and the times they had to be in, because I would go bananas they were-- you know, if I didn't know where they were.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe it's normal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- so it, it really hit me at that time that, uh, perhaps my upbringing, you know, wasn't quite what the normal course--",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
